text: Kedar Karki is a Nepalese politician and member of Provincial Assembly. Karki had served as the Chief Minister of Koshi Province15 October 2023 to 9 May 2024. He is also serving as member of Koshi Provincial Assembly having been elected from Morang 6 (B). == References == Category:Living people Category:Nepalese politicians Category:1974 births
title: Kedar Karki
